schools.name: Imogene Garner Hook Junior High School

data.description: Experience the perfect blend of rustic charm and modern convenience in this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom manufactured home. Tucked away on a generous 2.09-acre lot in a tranquil rural setting, this residence, constructed in 1995, seamlessly fuses comfortable indoor living with abundant outdoor amenities.     Step inside to discover a welcoming 1,654 square feet of living space. The home rests on a permanent foundation and features a versatile Quonset Hut, ideal for use as a workshop, garage, or storage space. Additionally, the property boasts a designated area equipped with power for accommodating an RV conveniently located on the property.
